To see docker images 
docker images

To search build images in docker- hub 
docker search imagename(Ubuntu)

To pull image form docker-hub
docker pull image name

To give name of container 
docker run - it  - - name nameofconatainer ubuntu sh or /bin/bash

To start a container 
docker start container name

To to process status for running container 
docker ps

To see all container process status
docker ps â€“ a

To go inside container 
docker attach container-nam

Create a image from existing container 
docker commit existing-container-name update-image-name

Create a new-container from this update-image
docker run - it  - - name  new-container update-image-name sh or /bin/bash

To stop container 
docker stop container-name

To remove container 
docker rm container-name

To remove image
docker rmi image-name
